                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3993Miracle">Miracle of Mary: unidentified miracle</title>, A miracle of Mary, very badly written.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez"/>
                                </item>

                                <item xml:id="a2" corresp="#h2">
                                    <locus from="130v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2739RepCh23">Malkǝʾa lǝdatā</title>, the following is the incipit:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ለልደትኪ፡ እግዝእትየ፡ <supplied resp="PRS10171Wright" reason="omitted">ማርያም፡</supplied>
                                        ቤዛዊተ፡ ቀርነ፡ ልዕልት፡ እስከ፡ አርያም፡</q>
                                </item>

                                <item xml:id="a3" corresp="#h2">
                                    <locus from="131r"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2940RepCh221">Malkǝʾ-hymn to Our Lady Mary</title>, the following is the incipit:</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ሰላም፡ ሰ<add place="above">ላ</add>ም፡ ለዝክረ፡ ስምኪ፡ በአምኃ፡ ሰርከ፡ ወነግሀ</q>
                                </item>

                            </list>
                        </additions>
                        
